I".<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>less +F <span class="nt">--follow-name</span> /var/log/mail.log
</code></pre></div></div>

<ul>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">ctrl+c</code> to stop streaming logfile</li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">/</code> to search</li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">F</code> to continue streaming logfile</li>
</ul>

